### Carbon Footprint API Testing

# Get current user's carbon footprint
GET http://localhost:5000/api/carbonfootprint/user/1

###

# Calculate carbon footprint for a trip
POST http://localhost:5000/api/carbonfootprint/calculate-trip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": 1,
  "distanceKm": 5.5
}

###

# Get leaderboard (top 10)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/carbonfootprint/leaderboard?topN=10

###

# Get leaderboard (top 20)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/carbonfootprint/leaderboard?topN=20

###

# Get user rank
GET http://localhost:5000/api/carbonfootprint/rank/1

###

# Calculate carbon for a different user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/carbonfootprint/calculate-trip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": 2,
  "distanceKm": 10.0
}

###

# Get updated leaderboard
GET http://localhost:5000/api/carbonfootprint/leaderboard

###

